  "description": "Deep cave acoustics — minerals ringing in their own resonant frequencies, undisturbed for millennia. High stiffness (0.82) and high formant intensity (0.90) give the crystal its character: brittle, specific, ringing. Slow 1.5-second attack and 4-second release create a sense of the instrument discovering you rather than you discovering it. Filter left semi-open to preserve the full mineral harmonic series.",
